{"title":"煤壁","authors":["王兆新"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":5,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王兆新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一名新矿工来到井下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对煤壁，注视不语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤壁是座黑色碑面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上边刻满了闪光的文字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他从未见过这种碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他从未读过这种碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种碑的存在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比人立的碑更气派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千名矿工一千种读音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但读出的内容却只有一种。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑眸子面对黑色煤壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注视之后，拜读之后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有民族的龙骨在体内生成。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}